transcripts: Hey sports fans, take a look at this great looking highlander picnic basket that includes your favorite NFL team right on the front. Whether you're going on a picnic or tailgating, this basket includes everything you'll need to have a great time. The highlander picnic basket is beautifully crafted from gruttan and bamboo and includes your team insignia right on the front. The inside is fully lined with this plaid. It has bows on the corners and cute ruffles all around. it's a complete service fro four and the design is really nice because everything has its place in the top here so you're neat and organized for your picnic. Let's talk about what comes with the picnic basket. It's a complete service of four. With these nice sized plates, four wine glasses, and service for four flatware. It also comes with this insulated wine bag, plastic container with a lid, this cute cheeseboard, corkscrew, and these adorable little salt and pepper shakers. It also comes with this cozy picnic blanket. It's everything you need for outdoor dining. Whether you're the sportsman or you're looking for the perfect gift for your favorite sports fan, this picnic basket with you're favorite NFL team is the perfect choice. The highlander basket is available online at Bed Bath and Beyond.
